databaseQueries.query: SELECT `anggarans`.`kategori_transaksi_id`, SUM(transaksis.jumlah) / anggarans.jumlah * 100 AS persentase FROM `transaksis` inner join `anggarans` on `transaksis`.`kategori_transaksi_id` = `anggarans`.`kategori_transaksi_id` WHERE `transaksis`.`user_id` = 32 and `transaksis`.`void` = 0 and `anggarans`.`user_id` = 32 and month(`transaksis`.`tanggal`) = '12' GROUP BY `transaksis`.`kategori_transaksi_id`, `anggarans`.`kategori_transaksi_id`, `anggarans`.`jumlah`, `transaksis`.`kategori_transaksi_id`
SELECT sum(`jumlah`) as aggregate FROM `transaksis` WHERE `user_id` = 32 and `jenis_transaksi_id` in (1, 4) and `void` = 0 and month(`tanggal`) = '12'
SELECT `nama`, `id`, (2500000 * value / 100) AS jumlah FROM `kategori_anggarans` WHERE `user_id` = 32
SELECT sum(`jumlah`) as aggregate FROM `transaksis` WHERE `user_id` = 32 and `jenis_transaksi_id` in (1, 4) and `void` = 0 and month(`tanggal`) = '12'

SELECT `kategori_anggarans`.`id` as `id_kategori_anggaran`, `kategori_anggarans`.`value`, SUM(transaksis.jumlah) as total_jumlah FROM `kategori_anggarans` left join `anggarans` on `kategori_anggarans`.`id` = `anggarans`.`kategori_anggaran_id` left join `transaksis` on `anggarans`.`kategori_transaksi_id` = `transaksis`.`kategori_transaksi_id` WHERE `anggarans`.`user_id` = 32 and `transaksis`.`user_id` = 32 and `transaksis`.`void` = 0 and month(`transaksis`.`tanggal`) = '12' GROUP BY `kategori_anggarans`.`id`, `kategori_anggarans`.`value`
SELECT * FROM `transaksis` WHERE `user_id` = 32 and `void` = 0 and month(`tanggal`) = '12'

SELECT `permissions`.*, `model_has_permissions`.`model_id` as `pivot_model_id`, `model_has_permissions`.`permission_id` as `pivot_permission_id`, `model_has_permissions`.`model_type` as `pivot_model_type` FROM `permissions` inner join `model_has_permissions` on `permissions`.`id` = `model_has_permissions`.`permission_id` WHERE `model_has_permissions`.`model_id` = 32 and `model_has_permissions`.`model_type` = 'App\\Models\\User'

SELECT `roles`.*, `model_has_roles`.`model_id` as `pivot_model_id`, `model_has_roles`.`role_id` as `pivot_role_id`, `model_has_roles`.`model_type` as `pivot_model_type` FROM `roles` inner join `model_has_roles` on `roles`.`id` = `model_has_roles`.`role_id` WHERE `model_has_roles`.`model_id` in (32) and `model_has_roles`.`model_type` = 'App\\Models\\User'
